{"tid":17452,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一次不忠 百次不用？","createTime":"2016-12-01T23:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T00:11:06.000Z","uid":49555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f0dd487b9e5890059a132eeefc87fdcf387205c","tid":17452,"uid":49555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T23:40:58.000Z","msg":"男朋友佢曾經試過同一個女仔拍拖拍左差唔多成年<br />\n而佢係差唔多同一時間同個女仔開始，又同我開始<br />\n點知。。。<br />\n我係兩年後先知。。。<br />\n真係好蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔會管人<br />\n所以我冇check 電話<br />\n又冇要佢報告果d<br />\n之前ex又係咁<br />\n其實點解我識親既人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係好傷心<br />\n就算佢話佢冇下次，會用時間證明<br />\n咁我心入面都係有條刺嘛<br />\n可以點<br />\n比左時間你啦<br />\n已經比左一年時間你<br />\n有用咩？<br />\n我唔覺得我可以忘記到<br />\n而且成日嘈交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次一嘈交<br />\n又賴落呢件事度<br />\n話我因為呢年事成日搵野黎嘈。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n永遠唔會係佢自己問題<br />\n講到我錯哂咁。。。。<br />\n唉。。。點解會有d 咁既人。。。<br />\n自己錯仲要推個責任落我度。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個人係咪其實係咪冇得發展<br />\nbtw,宜家同佢三年了"},{"pid":"d583592f0f13bd0feea0befee2507f987dac816a","tid":17452,"uid":39660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T23:45:09.000Z","msg":"分得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇將來"},{"pid":"119e629a8f59671bcb6636a06d2039474a453e74","tid":17452,"uid":45644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T23:47:53.000Z","msg":"斬纜啦&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\nbtw,有錢靚仔？"},{"pid":"29dc21b44c72f04f0dd2bd946846edc6b116326b","tid":17452,"uid":24519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T23:48:49.000Z","msg":"我以為你想講早洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"