0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T23:57:00.000Z","msg":"對方可以同一時間同兩個人開始 代表左兩個佢都唔係真係咁鍾意 衰d講句 可能plan a plan b<br />\n唔夠鍾意你既行為同表現 樓主應該feel到掛 點解要攬住個當你係次貨既人3年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一早應該分開 佢浪費緊你時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394916a7d3dddcf45bc01d0a478d893ced4e2912","tid":17452,"uid":49555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T23:58:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪有感情障礙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實咩叫感情障礙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b737e29c3a2cb3e1370c344e9c617a24a5bb66","tid":17452,"uid":17900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T00:00:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>斬啦...記得原因講淡咗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我都成日講過話想分手<br />\n但佢唔覺得淡左係一個原因。。。。<br />\n成日都唔肯分手。。。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢唔捨得冇西屌咋...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a3d24864813cb9ebb8961da09de459629ad19f5","tid":17452,"uid":49555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T00:05:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對方可以同一時間同兩個人開始 代表左兩個佢都唔係真係咁鍾意 衰d講句 可能plan a plan b<br />\n唔夠鍾意你既行為同表現 樓主應該feel到掛 點解要攬住個當你係次貨既人3年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一早應該分開 佢浪費緊你時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔明點解佢可以咁都得<br />\n佢地未分手果年我係feel 到佢唔夠中意我既<br />\n但果一年之後（當時我仲未知有呢件事）<br />\n又好似好d<br />\n其實果件事我真係唔知好過知。。。<br />\n好神奇既係。。。<br />\n果個女仔其實係佢地散左之後發現左<br />\n就已經fb msg 諗住話我知<br />\n但又唔知點解機緣巧合地。。。<br />\n我睇唔到，再過左一年我唔知禁咩禁禁下禁到個msg 出黎。。。<br />\n如果個女仔一msg 我果時我就發現<br />\n就唔洗因為唔捨得兩年感情而拖咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ddc9952e69de0f16f487d08c27d8f84b88e8d8","tid":17452,"uid":49555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T00:11:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>斬啦...記得原因講淡咗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我都成日講過話想分手<br />\n但佢唔覺得淡左係一個原因。。。。<br />\n成日都唔肯分手。。。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢唔捨得冇西屌咋...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我地冇乜點做。。。<br />\n佢話&quot;之前係做錯左，係想分又因為同個女仔有common fd 所以分唔成，做唔到太絕先拖左咁耐&quot;<br />\n佢話&quot;冇下次，我知道自己果次好錯&quot;之後係度喊喊喊<br />\n但果條刺。。我幾時先會冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 佢係我話分手，佢就死纏既人，所以我下下都分唔成。。"}]}